---
import experiences from "../collections/experiences.json";
import AboutExperience from "../components/about-experience.astro";
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="About Me"
      description="Hey there, I'm Kamal Wadhwa! 😊"
    />
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-10 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
    I'm an iOS developer from the vibrant city of Mumbai, India 🇮🇳. I have been passionately coding since 2007 and for work since 2012.
    </p>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-10 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
    When I'm not busy building beautiful apps, you'll catch me embracing my passions for fitness 🏋️, hitting scenic hiking trails 🏞, enjoying epic road trips 🚗, and exploring the globe 🌍.
  </p>
    <img src="/assets/images/about.jpg" class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 rounded-xl" />

    <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Short Bio</h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      Leads Platform at Heady. I'm an experienced iOS engineer who's built robust backend systems and slick native mobile apps completely from scratch. I thrive on taking product visions from concept to reality through end-to-end design and planning, all while leading and mentoring awesome teams. Passionate about the entire development ecosystem, I'm always geared up for the next exciting challenge! 😎🎉📱
    </p>

    <h2
      class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold lg:mt-10 sm:mt-6 dark:text-neutral-200"
    >
      Experience
    </h2>
    <div class="px-5 py-10">
      {
        experiences.map((experience) => {
          return (
            <div class="pb-10 border-l border-gray-200 last:border-l-0 dark:border-neutral-700">
              <AboutExperience
                dates={experience.dates}
                role={experience.role}
                company={experience.company}
                description={experience.description}
                logo={experience.logo}
              />
            </div>
          )
        })
      }
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold lg:mt-10 sm:mt-6 dark:text-neutral-200">Let's Connect</h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      If you want to stay up to date with my work be sure to <a
        href="https://x.com/iamkamalwadhwa"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-indigo-600 underline">follow me on twitter</a
      >, or you can send me an <a href="mailto:kamal.r.wadhwa@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline"
        >email</a
      > and I'll be sure to get back to you.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
